{"tid":346233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李彩華為演唱會性感解放！","createTime":"2017-08-03T18:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T19:05:54.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efd9466fe746ba0e3aff8fd541d7247411681f6c","tid":346233,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T18:44:00.000Z","msg":"李彩華（Rain）憑內地劇《回家的誘惑》走紅後，工作不斷身價水漲船高，Rain雖然在內地已貴為姐仔，但有小鮮肉見她在讀劇本培養情緒，串她演戲不用走心（意思不需用心），結果被Rain用演技當場KO。放下歌手身份多時，但Rain從未放棄唱歌，十月廿七日她將會回歸香港舉行首個演唱會，為這次處女演出，拍攝海報當日先來個性感解放。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/024010_dea568c5ec113fa7c14f7363693fc5d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F024010_dea568c5ec113fa7c14f7363693fc5d5.jpg&h=afaa0693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/024028_9b54b8a70997c06b83a338906222107b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F024028_9b54b8a70997c06b83a338906222107b.jpg&h=29c18806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2fc8Mfq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2fc8Mfq&d=YmV0dN6AzQ2jLWsh4HIT%2BgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c768f275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2fc8Mfq</a>"},{"pid":"35e56281fb506592d0e3bb695ad710d7ed42d793","tid":346233,"uid":17081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}